OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FA science teacher at a Catholic girls'
OL,7,Fschool in Liverpool who communicated
OL,8,Fwith pupils overnight and during the
OL,9,Fholidays has been banned from the
OL,10,Fprofession.
OL,12,FJennifer Farron was excluded from
OL,13,Fteaching indefinitely after
OL,14,Fdisciplinary proceedings found that
OL,15,Fshe "fostered a culture" in which her
OL,16,Fstudents could contact her in the
OL,17,Fmiddle of the night and "express
OL,18,Faffection" towards her.
OL,26,@wD@EOUwD@XO]yD@YOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
