CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779383153
OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FThe 34-year-old was employed at St
OL,7,FJohn Bosco Arts College from September
OL,8,F2017 before being suspended in June
OL,9,F2024.
OL,11,FThe investigation found "excessive"
OL,12,Fcommunication between Ms Farron and
OL,13,Ftwo students, including one pupil
OL,14,Femailing her at 2.14am to say that New
OL,15,FYear's Eve "was the worst 24 hours of
OL,16,F(their) life".
OL,18,FMs Farron was also found to have
OL,19,Fdeleted emails relevant to the
OL,20,Fallegations, and asked her students to
OL,21,Fdelete them too.
OL,26,@sD@YOUsD@cO]wD@LOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
