PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779383153
OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FIn the 90 days prior to the
OL,7,Fallegations being made in June 2024,
OL,8,FMs Farron had sent 79 emails to one
OL,9,Fpupil, and received 80 in return.
OL,11,FThose included that student telling Ms
OL,12,FFarron they "missed" her during the
OL,13,Fschool holidays.
OL,15,FMs Farron was also alleged to have
OL,16,Fencouraged a student to get a tattoo
OL,17,Flike hers, or visit her partner's cafe
OL,18,Foutside of school.
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
