FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779383153
OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FThe Teaching Regulation Agency found
OL,7,Fthat the communications outside of
OL,8,Fwork effectively blurred "a
OL,9,Fprofessional relationship with a more
OL,10,Fpersonal one".
OL,12,F"The panel considered that Ms Farron
OL,13,Fhad fostered a culture whereby pupils
OL,14,Ffelt they were able to send emails to
OL,15,Fher during the night and expressing
OL,16,Faffection towards her."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUrD@MO]tD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
