PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779383153
OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FMs Farron appeared to be talking to
OL,7,Fthem about issues they were
OL,8,Fexperiencing, and was found to have
OL,9,Fnot taken "appropriate action" to
OL,10,Fsafeguard "vulnerable" pupils.
OL,12,FEmails sent to and from pupils via
OL,13,Ftheir school accounts to Ms Farron
OL,14,Franged between 2.14am and 11.13pm.
OL,16,FShe admitted all of the allegations
OL,17,Fagainst her, but those relating to the
OL,18,Ftattoo and cafe were not proved by the
OL,19,Fpanel.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@^O]rD@KOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
