FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1779383153
OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FMs Farron told the panel that "with
OL,7,Fthe benefit of hindsight", there were
OL,8,Fthings she would do differently and
OL,9,Fshould have sought "further help" from
OL,10,Fher colleagues.
OL,12,FShe also said it "saddens" her that,
OL,13,F"anyone might think that I would do
OL,14,Fanything other than safeguard a child".
OL,16,FMs Farron has now been prohibited from
OL,17,Fteaching indefinitely in a decision
OL,18,Fhanded down on May 11 2026.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@YO]qD@TOUqD@aO]tD@ROUtD@ZO]uD@
OL,26,AAOUvD@fO]
