OL,3,CScience teacher struck off for
OL,4,Ccommunicating overnight with students
OL,6,FShe can apply for the prohibition
OL,7,Forder to be set aside but not until
OL,8,FMay 2029, and she has a right of
OL,9,Fappeal at the High Court.
